item.title: The Kid That Hung Himself Over Runescape
item.dc:creator: @Nashi Nashi
item.description:
@Nashi wrote:

I agree with scar, You guys arent seeing the big picture, most people hang themselves over problems with their parents or at school, this guy had both, I too have thought to myself, If there wasnt rs(which i enjoy playing to talk to FRIENDS), my friends, and my loved ones and if i were having problems then i would seriously consider suicide. This guy who had only his friend on rs, which then scammed him 11m, which to some can take quite a while to get(ive played 2 years onyl got 8m -.-), So he got fed up and killed himself. That isnt a laughing matter, Someone killed themself. Even if it was over something not too big, It was also about family and school. You should Have atleast some consideration for him.
